    <div class="moto-widget-text-content moto-widget-text-editable"><p class="moto-text_186">These are some of the requirements donors must meet to be eligible to donate blood based on their donation type.&nbsp;</p><p class="moto-text_186">&nbsp;</p><p class="moto-text_207"><span class="moto-color2_3">Blood Donation</span></p><p class="moto-text_207">&nbsp;</p><ul><li class="moto-text_normal"><span class="moto-color2_3">Donation frequency: After 3 Months</span></li><li class="moto-text_normal"><span class="moto-color2_3">You must be in good health and feeling well**</span></li><li class="moto-text_normal"><span class="moto-color2_3">You must be at least 18 years old </span></li><li class="moto-text_normal"><span class="moto-color2_3">You must weigh at least 50 kg</span></li></ul><p class="moto-text_normal">&nbsp;</p><p class="moto-text_186">If you have any questions regarding your eligibility, please call us at <a data-action="call" href="tel:1234567890">(123) 456 7890</a></p></div>
